Final [Oct 7]:
Alumni                4:0 Lomas Athletic             [at Porteño]
   [Lett 24, Eliseo Brown 35, 43, Campbell og 80]

Alumni won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:

Alumni:               José Buruca Laforia; Juan Domingo Brown, Jorge Gibson 
                      Brown; Andrés Arturo Mack, Carlos Buchanan, Patricio 
                      Barron Browne; Gottlob Eduardo Weiss, Carlos Lett, Arnaldo
                      Pencliffe Watson Hutton, Ernesto Alejandro Brown, Eliseo 
                      Brown. 
 
